pg_promoter
===========

pg_promoter is simplified clustring module based on bgworker.

- How to install pg_promoter
Note that pg_promoter works fine only slave server side.

$ mv pg_promoter postgresql/contrib/
$ cd postgresql/contrib
$ make
# make install

- How to use pg_promoter

$ vi postgresql.conf
shared_preload_libraries = 'pg_promoter'
pg_promoter.keepalive = 5
pg_promoter.primary_conninfo = 'host=192.168.100.100 port=5432'
